title: 1Password 4 [Zeus Downloads]
description:
1Password 4
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: https://agilebits.com/onepassword/mac


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "1Password 4.dmg"
- Drag/Copy "1Password.app" to your "Applications" folder.
- Thats it, you now have a fully functional copy of 1Password 4.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update 1Password 4 as updating it might cause a problem. You have been warned.
